{"type":"text","timestamp":1781151255030,"sessionID":"ses_14b1d6f21ffeiA9vRmpnyEZ4DQ","part":{"id":"prt_eb4e349b3001JZlFnFP3Y74xiS","messageID":"msg_eb4e31610001XiFUzlv6oGI1UV","sessionID":"ses_14b1d6f21ffeiA9vRmpnyEZ4DQ","type":"text","text":"SKILL ROUTING: User directed → `deep-review`. The loaded contract forbids nested dispatch and self-invoked `opencode run`; I’ll execute this lineage as the already-dispatched leaf by creating the required state, iteration, and synthesis artifacts directly under the override artifact directory.","time":{"start":1781151254963,"end":1781151255029},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_00e2e3574c078a7e016a2a3616f5b08191bfbb739a2bafa20e","phase":"commentary"}}}}
