{"type":"text","timestamp":1781151319644,"sessionID":"ses_14b1d6f21ffeiA9vRmpnyEZ4DQ","part":{"id":"prt_eb4e438e60014UglmI5o92BT0z","messageID":"msg_eb4e41933001paZ6jKsv4GY7oN","sessionID":"ses_14b1d6f21ffeiA9vRmpnyEZ4DQ","type":"text","text":"The existing fault-injection test checks the rebuilt shard file from a new connection, but it does not verify the still-running daemon connection can query the rebuilt vectors after the rename. That leaves the attach/rename concern active.","time":{"start":1781151316198,"end":1781151319642},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0d9d167ebf797419016a2a365430448191b0de8fb6ec352993","phase":"commentary"}}}}
